 0x1: 无线充电器关闭
 0x2: 无线充电器打开
 0x3：无效
 CWC收到DVD的0x0、0x3时保持CWC当前开关状态
     * VehiclePropertyChangeMode:ON_CHANGE
     * VehiclePropertyAccess:WRITE
     * Signal Value:
        0x0:Not active
         0x1:OFF
         0x2:ON
         0x3:Invalid
     */
    ICC_CWCWORKINGSTSSET_4E6 = (
        0x164B
        | VehiclePropertyGroup:VENDOR
        | VehiclePropertyType:INT32
        | VehicleArea:GLOBAL),

